19. What is binding?
Linking method call to method body.
Binding means how a method call is connected to its actual implementation at runtime or compile time.
In simple, When you call a method, how does PHP decide which method to execute? That process is called binding.

PHP mainly has 2 types:
1. Early Binding (Static Binding)
2. Late Binding (Dynamic Binding)

Q. What is Late Static Binding?
